               <code code="42232-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="PRECAUTIONS SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <caption styleCode="bold">Caution:</caption> Folic Acid may partially correct the hematological damage due to Vitamin B-12 deficiency of pernicious anemia while the associated neurological damage progresses.
      

 </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20200519"/>
            </section>
