               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <caption styleCode="bold">WARNING: Accidental overdose of iron-containing products is a leading cause of fatal poisoning in children under six. KEEP THIS PRODUCT OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. In case of accidental overdose, call a physician or Poison Control Center immediately.</caption>
